name: PNW Data Managers
tagline: A community of folks in the PNW looking to SAVE THE DATA!
body:
### Welcome to PNW Data Managers! 
---

#### WHO WE ARE
We are librarians, data scientists, researchers, open research advocates and so much more.  

#### WHERE WE ARE
We are scattered across the PNW... British Columbia, Idaho, Montana, Oregon, & Washington

#### WHAT WE DO
Come find out at our upcoming meeting in Vancouver at Simon Fraser University!!!  
SAVE THE DATE! November 10, 2016  
More details forthcoming...
